text: Bürgermeister Anna is an East German comedy film directed by Hans Müller. It was released in 1950. ==Cast== * Eva Rimski as Anna Drews * Reinhard Kolldehoff as Jupp Ucker * Catja Görna as Ursel Ucker * Klaus Becker as Hans Rapp * Arno Paulsen as Bauer Lehmkuhl * Lutz Moik as Matthias Lehmkuhl * Arthur Wiesner as Vater Ucker * Steffie Spira as Mutter Ucker * Charlotte Ritter as Mutter Drews * Gustav Püttjer as Ohm Willem * Erich Dunskus as Bauer Rau * Edith Hancke as Grete Drews * Sigrid Lagemann as Elli Rapp ==External links== * Category:1950 films Category:1950 comedy films Category:German comedy films Category:East German films Category:German-language films Category:German black-and-white films
